sequenceDiagram
    participant Cron as core/run scheduler
    participant News as news scraper
    participant Price as token price fetcher
    participant Research as research jobs
    participant Quant as signal-detector
    participant FinBERT as HuggingFace FinBERT
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Layer3 as layer3 workflow
    participant Gemini as Google Gemini
    participant API as /api/signals and /api/proposals
    participant UI as Next.js UI

    Cron->>News: npm run news
    News->>DB: upsert news_articles
    Cron->>Price: npm run prices:backfill:1d
    Price->>DB: write token_prices and token_price_history
    Cron->>Research: run backtest, metrics, regime, weights
    Research->>DB: update backtest_results, rolling_metrics, weights
    Cron->>Quant: npm run signal
    Quant->>DB: read tweets, news_articles, tokens, history
    Quant->>FinBERT: score document sentiment
    FinBERT-->>Quant: sentiment scores
    Quant->>Quant: aggregate by token and evaluate alpha
    Quant->>DB: insert signals with status RAW
    Cron->>Layer3: npm run layer3
    Layer3->>DB: claim RAW signal as PROCESSING
    Layer3->>DB: resolve source content from tweets and news_articles
    Layer3->>Gemini: generate Vietnamese rationale
    Gemini-->>Layer3: rationaleSummary
    Layer3->>DB: upsert active proposal and mark signal PROCESSED
    UI->>API: GET /api/signals or /api/proposals
    API->>DB: read signals, proposals and backtest fields
    DB-->>API: enriched records
    API-->>UI: signal and proposal payload
